be an expansion of \(\hat{W}\) in the number basis. Then

\[
\hat{W}_{i,k_1}^T = \sum_{n',m',n'',m''=0}^{\infty} \alpha_{n' m' n'' m''} |n'\rangle_i \langle m'| \otimes |m''\rangle_{k_1} \langle n''|.
\]

By a direct calculation, one can demonstrate that

\[
\hat{I}_i \otimes \hat{W}_{j,k_1} \sum_{n'=0}^{\infty} |n'\rangle_i |n'\rangle_j \otimes |\psi\rangle_{k_1,\ldots,k_n} = \hat{W}_{i,k_1}^T \otimes \hat{I}_j \sum_{n'=0}^{\infty} |n'\rangle_i |n'\rangle_j \otimes |\psi\rangle_{k_1,\ldots,k_n}.
\]

